Package: hte3
Type: Package
Title: Causal Machine Learning for Heterogeneous Treatment Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lars van der Laan
Maintainer: Lars van der Laan <lvdlaan@uw.edu>
Description: Tools for estimating heterogeneous treatment effects using
    supervised causal machine learning. The package provides low-level
    learner classes built on top of the 'sl3' and 'tmle3' ecosystems,
    along with higher-level task construction and model fitting helpers
    for conditional average treatment effects and conditional risk ratios.
